NAME: System Integration Analyst
DESCRIPTION: System Integration Analyst has access to public information widely available for integarting to Oracle E-Business Suite. This level of information less detailed as compared to that available to a System Integration Developer.

NAME: Partner Administrator
DESCRIPTION: Represents external people that manage user accounts and access for people in their own as well as any partner organizations.

NAME: Customer Administrator
DESCRIPTION: Represents external people that manage user accounts / access for people in their own organization (defined as organization parties).
